The '''Inner Mongolia Radio Broadcasting Network''' ({{zh|c=内蒙古广播网|p=Nèiménggǔ Guǎngbò Wǎng}}; {{lang-mn|ᠥᠪᠦᠷ ᠮᠣᠩᠭᠣᠯ ᠤᠨ ᠷᠠᠳᠢᠣ᠋ ᠰᠦᠯᠵᠢᠶ᠎ᠡ}}) is a [[radio broadcasting]] network headquartered in [[Hohhot]], [[Inner Mongolia|Inner Mongolia Autonomous Region]] of the [[China|People's Republic of China]]. It was founded in 1950.
